2) Install opencv if you do not have!!

3) Install python if you do not have!! 


------

To run the sensor

1) Power the sensor then you should see three LEDs:  Red, Blue, and Yellow
If Blue blinking, then something wrong!!! --> ask Alin
 
2) Connect tactileAP , password tactile0

3) check IP, .100 
Setup IP address

IP 192.168.100
Netmask 255.255.255.0

4) Run the program
poma@poma-HP-EliteBook-840-G1:~/workspace/pmanoonpong-gorobots-fork/examples/sensors/tactile$ python ctakt_multiple.py 

poma@poma-HP-EliteBook-840-G1:~/workspace/pmanoonpong-gorobots-fork/examples/sensors/tactile$ python ctakt_multiple.py 
